:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9e67a1082671adf066f8ba9044efca672f72bab","tid":1513834,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45b5d20c056f26691f330388d5e0d6485a3eb7c","tid":1513834,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:57:31.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">五 大 訴 求   缺 一 不 可</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"a3b40b1187a3222640d41e6da054ec47e2b8880e","tid":1513834,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>香港都大火呀！<br />\n燒咗兩個幾月啦！<br />\n擘大隻眼睇下依家發生緊咩事啦！<br />\n你仲好唔好意思唔企出嚟呀？</strong></span>"},{"pid":"161a38241f3dee01eb6e47726c9c8015020d9378","tid":1513834,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得當初812我地點解要入機場<br />\n<br />\n依家係警察不停開槍射頭射眼，仲大條道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>黑 警 還 眼</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔只係口號咁簡單，我地要警察為佢地做過嘅事負責<br />\n<br />\n812咁成功，因為你同我都有參與<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地901一齊入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記得係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1PM</span></span> 到機場吖<br />\n<br />\n誓要討回公道、要政府正面回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q：可能你會問，機場出咗禁制令，點解仲要入機場？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA：<br />\n禁制令=藐視法庭最多判幾月內(黃之峰坐左)<br />\n<br />\n非法集結起步判幾月<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪起步判3年以上至6年(梁天琦坐緊)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非法集會嚴重過藐視法庭啊</span></span><br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n明白個遊戲點玩未？？<br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜都咁多手足俾人拉咗，分分鐘坐幾年甚至十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你真係甘心佢地咁努力，然後我地白費曬佢地嘅心機？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有勇氣上街頭勇武<br />\n點解唔敢入機場？</span>"},{"pid":"219f03b8c5875d142c55e6a84b515b52ff1cf4ff","tid":1513834,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"161a38241f3dee01eb6e47726c9c8015020d9378","tid":1513834,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:57:51.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得當初812我地點解要入機場<br />\n<br />\n依家係警察不停開槍射頭射眼，仲大條道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>黑 警 還 眼</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔只係口號咁簡單，我地要警察為佢地做過嘅事負責<br />\n<br />\n812咁成功，因為你同我都有參與<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地901一齊入機場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記得係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1PM</span></span> 到機場吖<br />\n<br />\n誓要討回公道、要政府正面回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q：可能你會問，機場出咗禁制令，點解仲要入機場？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA：<br />\n禁制令=藐視法庭最多判幾月內(黃之峰坐左)<br />\n<br />\n非法集結起步判幾月<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪起步判3年以上至6年(梁天琦坐緊)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非法集會嚴重過藐視法庭啊</span></span><br />\n___________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n明白個遊戲點玩未？？<br />\n<br />\n每個禮拜都咁多手足俾人拉咗，分分鐘坐幾年甚至十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你真係甘心佢地咁努力，然後我地白費曬佢地嘅心機？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有勇氣上街頭勇武<br />\n點解唔敢入機場？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:58:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">求幫推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【突發】【有圖】機場手足已淪為condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510519\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9ed26d4d4169e1a589b29f9297c731359475dd9","tid":1513834,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d24f55ee8eaeef98f500274fcf59f13d7f71628a","tid":1513834,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04fc71ca003fa48d9b5662891c402c1ad23668bd","tid":1513834,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bba9514deebe955abcf8eeab7dfebb1d587f8f2","tid":1513834,"uid":276989,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:12:36.000Z","msg":"全香港都知，係中央唔知姐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:32:14.000Z","msg":"事實. 我都知. 只係中共唔知. <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:25:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>不能排除成家人都係英國人既林奠係英國間諜，係中國、美英共同協商之下可以管治香港的選擇，記唔記得主權換治權? 中共表面反對，實質上隔一段時間就有英國代表做特首(曾蔭權、林奠) 。留意689曾經都被中方認為係英國間諜。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong>"},{"pid":"fe1684fbe11f6332f08a82ac15ef8bdd7d16d403","tid":1513834,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ca21e6297da80cb037f6dd75b831156c67e3f9","tid":1513834,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9ed26d4d4169e1a589b29f9297c731359475dd9","tid":1513834,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d24f55ee8eaeef98f500274fcf59f13d7f71628a","tid":1513834,"uid":276971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04fc71ca003fa48d9b56628